{"tid":1425994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 時代革命宣言","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:11:22.000Z","uid":160508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"670efc120a09465053c1f7b80a708aeda5b83466","tid":1425994,"uid":160508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:06:12.000Z","msg":"利申：和理非<br />\n柒婆依家出嚟想分裂我哋<br />\n仲捉住個口號想扣我哋帽子<br />\n個人認為有需要寫返個革命宣言<br />\n清楚講俾所有人聽我哋要嘅係咩<br />\n就咁話5大訴求已經唔夠<br />\n我哋需要一個大方向<br />\n需要一個可以connect所有人嘅宣言<br />\n<br />\n提議：<br />\nopen source 一份革命宣言<br />\n列出我哋點解要抗爭<br />\n我哋嘅訴求係乜嘢<br />\n話俾全世界知咩叫 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n然後公開匿名投票去改編<br />\n直到有份stable copy<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<br />\n點睇？"},{"pid":"97ab14673cb177d687f278c02421f5fecc667059","tid":1425994,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081110_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081110_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=edf017c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081112_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081112_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png&h=8aeaf4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081119_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081119_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=73201278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081120_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081120_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png&h=09aede10&s={SIZE}\" /><i